LMR 8.1

data("pipeline")

mod1 <- lm(Lab ~ Field, data=pipeline)
plot(mod1)

i <- order(pipeline$Field)
npipe <- pipeline[i,]
ff <- gl(12,9)[-108]
meanfield <- unlist(lapply(split(npipe$Field, ff), mean))
varlab <- unlist(lapply(split(npipe$Lab, ff), var))

modEst <- lm(log(varlab) ~ log(meanfield))$coef
mod2 <- lm(Lab ~ Field, data=pipeline, weights=modEst[2]*pipeline$Field - modEst[1]*pipeline$Lab)
summary(mod2)
## 
## Call:
## lm(formula = Lab ~ Field, data = pipeline, weights = modEst[2] * 
##     pipeline$Field - modEst[1] * pipeline$Lab)
## 
## Weighted Residuals:
